      <h2 class="h2">[Why a Charter?]</h2>
      <img class="block__promo block__promo--right" data-src="holder.js/320x320?text=Promo Image" />
      <p>There are lots of lovely people across Manchester who are working hard, or willing, to help support people who are homeless.  Think of the Charter as your membership to join one big happy family: the Charter is a way to bring us all together, giving us one shared vision and a platform to link up our resources and skills.  This means we can focus our efforts efficiently and effectively to tackle key challenges and ultimately move towards banishing homelessness.</p>
