      <h2 class="h2">Latest news</h2>
      <img class="block__promo block__promo--left" data-src="holder.js/320x320?text=Promo Image" />
      <p>The Charter will launch on 9th May at Friend’s Meeting House.</p>
      <p>Presented by the Bishop of Manchester and attended by Richard Leese, leader of Manchester City Council, this will be a historic event which celebrates the commitment of our city’s people, organisations and businesses to tackling homelessness. A symbolic handing over from the Manchester Homelessness Partnership to homeless people will be part of the launch and there’ll be opportunities to pledge your support and join an action group too.</p>
      <p>For more information, please contact <a href="mailto:charter@streetsupport.net">charter@streetsupport.net</a></p>
